<p class="intro">Receive a concierge-style experience from the CES broadcast team, who will work with you before your on-site arrival to determine your particular needs, so that you can get to the show, plug in and be on the air!</p>  

<p>Here&#39;s a brief rundown of what our broadcast team can provide:</p>

